<p>I was reading about the upcoming legislation regarding Alzheimer's. I am very happy our Government is taking steps to address this upcoming tsunami called Alzheimer's that is going to hit our country. I am not sure where to start? so i will start at the beginning my Mother was diagnosed 11 years ago with Alzheimer's.</p>
